Touch with extreme care: `_contact_find_title_sweep_for_enquiry`, `_contact_mobile_drilldown_plans`, `_click_nth_mobile_title_drilldown`, `_siebel_ui_suggests_contact_match_mobile_first`, `_contact_enquiry_tab_has_rows`, mobile-only fallbacks, ordinal ≥1 drills, re-find between duplicates.
